high_descs: Turn left and walk to the apple on the counter to the left.
Take the knife on the left.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the door, slice the tomato on the shelf, and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the stove on the left.
Put the knife in the pan on the right.
Turn left and walk back to the fridge on the right.
Open the door. take a tomato slice on the shelf, and close the door.
Turn right and walk back to the stove on the left.
Place the tomato in the pan with the knife on the right.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn left, take a step, the turn right and walk to the counter.
Place the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife and tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, pass the refrigerator, turn to the counter on the left.
Pick up the butter knife next to the apple in the back.
Walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, cut the stem off of the tomato.
Close the refrigerator door, walk to the stove.
Put the butter knife in the skillet.
Go back to refrigerator.
Take the tomato slice out of the bottom of the refrigerator.
Go back to the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the skillet.
Pick up the skillet off of the stove.
Take a step to the left.
Put the skillet on the counter in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice into the skillet on the counter with a butter knife.

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter by the stove to your left.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge, cut the green part off of the tomato inside and close the fridge.
Turn right then face the stove to your left.
Place the knife in the pot on the stove to the right.
Turn left then face the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge in front of you, take out a tomato slice and close the fridge.
Turn right then face the stove to your left.
Place the tomato slice in the pot with the knife in front of you.
Take the pot with the tomato slice in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter on your right.
Place the pot with the tomato on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a tomato slice on the counter by the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the butter knife from the very back of the counter.
Turn to the left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, use the butter knife to cut the tomato into slices, then close the fridge.
Turn to the right and go down to the stove on the left.
Put the butter knife in the blue pan on the back right stove burner.
Turn to the left and head back to the fridge.
Open the fridge, pick up a slice of tomato, and close the fridge.
Turn to the right and head back to the stove.
Put the tomato in the blue pan with the butter knife.
Pick up the blue pan that has the butter knife and tomato in it.
Turn to the left and go to the counter between the stove and the fridge.
Set the blue pan on the counter on the left side of the apple closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a cold tomato and a butter knife in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and stop at the counter to the left of the stove
Grab the knife that is on the counter
Turn left and stop at the fridge
Open the bottom door of the fridge and cut the tomato in the fridge in slices Close the door
Turn right and stop at the oven
Place the knife in the pan on the top right stove
Turn left and head to the fridge
Open the  bottom door of the fridge and grab one of the tomato slices. Close the door
Turn right and head to the oven
Put the tomato in the pan in the top right stove
Grab the pan with the knife and tomato in it
Turn slightly left and stop at the counter
Place the pan down on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan with a knife and tomato slice in it on the counter
